origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['GoldInvestment.get_investment_methods', {'name': 'GoldInvestment.get_investment_methods', 'description': 'This function provides basic methods for investing in gold.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'methods', 'description': 'A list of methods for investing in gold, including details on each method.'}]}], ['GoldInvestment.get_recent_price_trends', {'name': 'GoldInvestment.get_recent_price_trends', 'description': 'This function retrieves recent price trends for gold.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration for which to retrieve price trends, e.g., 1 month, 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'trends', 'description': 'A chart or data showing the price trends of gold over the specified duration.'}]}], ['GoldInvestment.analyze_price_factors', {'name': 'GoldInvestment.analyze_price_factors', 'description': 'This function analyzes the main factors affecting gold prices.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'factors', 'description': 'An analysis of the factors that significantly impact gold prices.'}]}], ['GoldInvestment.suggest_investment_timing', {'name': 'GoldInvestment.suggest_investment_timing', 'description': 'This function suggests the best timing for gold investment based on risk tolerance.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'risk_tolerance', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The investor’s risk tolerance level, e.g., low, medium, high.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'timing', 'description': 'A suggestion on the best timing for gold investment based on the investor’s risk tolerance.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `GoldInvestment.get_investment_methods`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "GoldInvestment.get_investment_methods",
    "args": "{}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
